#. <section class="sutta" id="sn56.24"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn56.24:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 56"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 56"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.24:0.2"
msgid "3. Koṭigāmavagga"
msgstr "3. At the Village of Koṭi"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn56.24:0.3"
msgid "24. Arahantasutta"
msgstr "24. The Perfected Ones"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.434"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.24:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn56.24:1.2"
msgid ""
"“Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, atītamaddhānaṃ arahanto sammāsambuddhā yathābhūtaṃ "
"abhisambujjhiṃsu, sabbe te cattāri ariyasaccāni yathābhūtaṃ abhisambujjhiṃsu."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, whatever perfected ones, fully awakened Buddhas truly wake up—"
"in the past,"

#. VAR: hi → yepi hi (s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "sn56.24:1.3"
msgid ""
"Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, anāgatamaddhānaṃ arahanto sammāsambuddhā yathābhūtaṃ "
"abhisambujjhissanti, sabbe te cattāri ariyasaccāni yathābhūtaṃ "
"abhisambujjhissanti."
msgstr "future,"

msgctxt "sn56.24:1.4"
msgid ""
"Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, etarahi arahanto sammāsambuddhā yathābhūtaṃ "
"abhisambujjhanti, sabbe te cattāri ariyasaccāni yathābhūtaṃ abhisambujjhanti."
msgstr "or present—all of them truly wake up to the four noble truths."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.24:2.1"
msgid "Katamāni cattāri?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "sn56.24:2.2"
msgid ""
"Dukkhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ, dukkhasamudayaṃ ariyasaccaṃ, dukkhanirodhaṃ "
"ariyasaccaṃ, dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā ariyasaccaṃ."
msgstr ""
"The noble truths of suffering, the origin of suffering, the cessation of "
"suffering, and the practice that leads to the cessation of suffering."

msgctxt "sn56.24:2.3"
msgid ""
"Ye hi, keci, bhikkhave, atītamaddhānaṃ arahanto sammāsambuddhā yathābhūtaṃ "
"abhisambujjhiṃsu … pe …"
msgstr ""
"Whatever perfected ones, fully awakened Buddhas truly wake up—in the past,"

msgctxt "sn56.24:2.4"
msgid "abhisambujjhissanti …"
msgstr "future,"

msgctxt "sn56.24:2.5"
msgid ""
"abhisambujjhanti, sabbe te imāni cattāri ariyasaccāni yathābhūtaṃ "
"abhisambujjhanti."
msgstr "or present—all of them truly wake up to the four noble truths."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.24:3.1"
msgid ""
"Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yogo karaṇīyo … pe … ‘ayaṃ "
"dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yogo karaṇīyo”ti."
msgstr "That’s why you should practice meditation …”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.24:3.2"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
